t:
I found some gold coins while digging in the garden.

I got so excited that I ran inside to tell my mother all about it,




but then I remembered why I was digging.
c:
I'm surprised, I didn't find any coins when digging for my father.
Anyways, she was a #golddigger.



#garden #digging  #gold #surprise #childish #forgetting #mentalhealth
